# This is a PUBLIC repo. Raw camera/phone originals must NOT be committed:
# they embed EXIF GPS (the house's location) + timestamps, and bloat git history.
# Drop raw files into a local _originals/ folder — it stays out of git.
# Only the optimised, metadata-stripped .webp assets get committed.
_originals/
**/_originals/

# Belt-and-braces: never commit these source / raw types anywhere under images/
*.heic
*.HEIC
*.heif
*.tif
*.tiff
*.dng
*.cr2
*.nef
*.arw
*.psd
